Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:38.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,这辆车真是太棒了\N{\fs90}This thing's bloody awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:41.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,听听他的吼叫声\N{\fs90}Listen to that bellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:43.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,车身深深的坐进了底盘上\N{\fs90}This thing squats on its haunches
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,它就是为此而造的\N{\fs90}This is what it's built to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:48.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,每一次噼里啪啦砰砰磅磅的声音\N{\fs90}Every crackle, pop and bang
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:52.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,都会通过每根神经直接传给我\N{\fs90}is just connected to every synapse and sinew in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 不是吧\N{\fs90}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:05.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就好比第一次约会的时候\N{\fs90}This is like a first date for me, and on a first date,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:08.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不希望女孩的秃顶胖叔叔全程尾随\N{\fs90}you don't want a fat,balding uncle tagging along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:13.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我现在要做的就是 甩掉他\N{\fs90}So what I'm gonna do now... is lose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:20.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,接招吧 尝尝我的厉害\N{\fs90}It's Hammer Time!Shock and awe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:31.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,邦德 大战 伯恩\N{\fs90}It's Bond versus Bourne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:41.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,他那辆排量5.0 而我只有2.3\N{\fs90}He's got five litres.I've only got 2.3.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:45.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,可他的速度有我2倍快吗 并没有\N{\fs90}Is he going twice as fast?No, he is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:51.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,前面是弯道\N{\fs90}Corner coming up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.17,字幕,,0,0,0,, 开着野马再也不用担惊受怕了\N{\fs90}There's no need to panic any more in a Mustang,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:54.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为 野马史无前例的\N{\fs90}because, for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,装备了后独立悬挂\N{\fs90}the Mustang has independent rear suspension.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:09.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,这辆车的过弯速度\N{\fs90}The cornering speeds this thing can achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,令人不敢相信\N{\fs90}beggar belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:24.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车的抓地力怎么这么强\N{\fs90}How does it grip that well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:31.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,我正开着野马进行飞车追逐\N{\fs90}I'm in a car chase in a Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:33.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就是史蒂夫 麦奎因\N{\fs90}I am Steve McQueen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:40.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,尝尝这招\N{\fs90}Try that on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,我切换到了运动模式\N{\fs90}I've got it in Sport Mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,能让排气轰隆作响\N{\fs90}which makes the exhaust pop and bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:59.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天哪\N{\fs90}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:01.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,油门到底\N{\fs90}Flat out, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:05.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,抓地力太惊人\N{\fs90}And it still grips!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:10.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车没必要加牵引力控制系统\N{\fs90}What is the point of traction control on this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:13.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,就好像给修女戴贞操带一样没意义\N{\fs90}It's like putting a nymphomania control on a nun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.06,0:22:25.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 坏了\N{\fs90}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:41.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,他跑哪儿去了\N{\fs90}Where's he gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不可能 他开着那辆18世纪的老古董\N{\fs90}How did he do that? How did he get away from me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:49.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,是怎么甩掉我的\N{\fs90}in something from the 18th century?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:51.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且我还开着\N{\fs90}Especially when I'm driving
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:55.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,一辆带涡轮增压的藤壶\N{\fs90}what is basically a turbocharged barnacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:23:00.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,这辆车拥有最精密的四驱系统\N{\fs90}This has the most sophisticated four-wheel-drive system
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:02.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,谁都比不上\N{\fs90}fitted to any car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:07.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,GTR的四驱都比不上它\N{\fs90}Not even a Nissan GTR could live with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:15.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,那辆野马就好比听着唐 亨利\N{\fs90}The Mustang, well, that's for cruising down
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.38,0:23:19.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,在太平洋海岸公路上巡航\N{\fs90}the Pacific Coast Highway,listening to Don Henley.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:22.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,而这辆车就像是听着Clash乐队\N{\fs90}This is for storming up the Stelvio Pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:24.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,在斯泰尔维奥山口公路飞驰\N{\fs90}listening to the Clash.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:31.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管如此新潮且充满高科技\N{\fs90}But while it's a grippy,technological masterpiece,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.33,0:23:36.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,但它依旧保留着祖辈的蓝领性格\N{\fs90}it still has the blue-collar character of its ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:37.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,它在很多地方 \N{\fs90}In many ways
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:40.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,都让我想起了当年的Escort Cosworth \N{\fs90}this reminds me of the old Escort Cosworth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.54,0:23:42.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,那可是辆伟大的车\N{\fs90}and that was a great car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.14,0:23:44.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,我在90年代有一辆 我叫它Gary\N{\fs90}I actually had one in the '90s. I called it Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.95,0:23:46.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,每天早上我打火 它会问候我\N{\fs90}It started every morning and it always went
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:48.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,"今儿要去干嘛"\N{\fs90}"Do you want some?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:51.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,口气就像是长了雨刷的约翰 特里\N{\fs90}It was just John Terry, really, with windscreen wipers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.56,0:23:58.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,与此同时 在成功甩掉大猩猩以后\N{\fs90}Meanwhile,having got rid of the ape,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:01.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,我继续带着野马四处观光\N{\fs90}I was back on my sightseeing tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:03.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是我们的切达峡谷\N{\fs90}This is our Cheddar Gorge.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:07.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,很明显没有你们的峡谷大\N{\fs90}Obviously it's not as big as your gorge.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:09.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,科罗拉多大峡谷要更大一些\N{\fs90}The Grand Canyon is bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:13.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,更长 更深 也更广阔\N{\fs90}Well, it's longer and deeper... and wider.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.27,0:24:15.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,但那里没有奶酪\N{\fs90}Mm. But it doesn't have any cheese in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.98,0:24:18.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,你别来烦我行吗\N{\fs90}Why can't you just leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.05,0:24:18.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 \N{\fs90}I'm just saying
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:20.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,在美国 所有东西里都会加奶酪\N{\fs90} everything in America comes with cheese
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:22.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,除了科罗拉多大峡谷\N{\fs90}apart from the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:25.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而这座峡谷却出产奶酪 \N{\fs90}Whereas this canyon does come with cheese
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.09,0:24:25.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,还很好吃\N{\fs90}and it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.99,0:24:27.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你也吃点 -我不想吃奶酪\N{\fs90}-Here, have some.-I don't want cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:29.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,比蒙特里杰克好吃多了\N{\fs90}-It's better than Monterey Jack in a tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.52,0:24:30.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,你毁了我的节目\N{\fs90}-You're ruining this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.78,0:24:33.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,你才是呢 因为你在告诉所有人\N{\fs90}No, you are, because you are telling everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.26,0:24:37.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,野马比福克斯要强\N{\fs90}that the Mustang is better than the Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.80,0:24:39.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,-本来就是 -并不是\N{\fs90}-Well, it is.-It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.70,0:24:41.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是这样 -不是\N{\fs90}-It is.-No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.36,0:24:44.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,听着 我并不是说福克斯很完美 \N{\fs90}Look, I'm not saying this is perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.40,0:24:45.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,它确实不是\N{\fs90}cos it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.51,0:24:47.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,它开起来很颠 \N{\fs90}There's a vertical choppiness to the ride
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.56,0:24:48.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,这点很讨厌\N{\fs90}which is annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.74,0:24:50.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你把手机放在\N{\fs90}If you put your phone in the phone holder
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.71,0:24:51.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,档把前面的槽里\N{\fs90} in front of the gear lever
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.77,0:24:54.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,在加速的时候手机会飞到座椅下面\N{\fs90}and then accelerate,it shoots under the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.11,0:24:55.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,你就再也见不到它了\N{\fs90}You never see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.32,0:24:57.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,油箱实在是太小了\N{\fs90}Petrol tank, way too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.28,0:25:00.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且它的风格有点粗鲁 \N{\fs90}-And the styling is a bit...yobbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.17,0:25:00.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,有点而已吗\N{\fs90}-A bit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.92,0:25:02.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是哈蒙德 看这里\N{\fs90}But, Hammond, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.11,0:25:07.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 你说得对\N{\fs90}Oh, yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.33,0:25:09.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,野马拥有半个世纪的历史 \N{\fs90}Half a century of Mustang history
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.83,0:25:11.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,传承和骄傲\N{\fs90}heritage and pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.43,0:25:14.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,却没有想到在门上加一块小塑料片\N{\fs90}but it hasn't got a small plastic strip on the door
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.53,0:25:16.04,字幕,,0,0,0,, 以防你笨手笨脚磕到门\N{\fs90}in case you're a bit clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.10,0:25:19.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,但这个设计太巧秒了 而且它还更快\N{\fs90}No, it's brilliant, that. And... this is faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.74,0:25:21.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 我的更快\N{\fs90}Well, no, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.94,0:25:24.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我的快 -不 我的\N{\fs90}-It is.-No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.69,0:25:27.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,-就是我的快 -是我\N{\fs90}-It is.-It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.35,0:25:30.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,事已至此 我决定放弃我的行程\N{\fs90}At this point,I decided to abandon my tour
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.98,0:25:33.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,到最近的机场\N{\fs90}and head for the nearest airfield...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.80,0:25:36.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,给大猩猩上一课\N{\fs90}...to teach Clarkson a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.02,0:25:44.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,好了 我有410匹马力\N{\fs90}Right,I've got 410 horsepower -
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.06,0:25:45.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,比他要多100匹\N{\fs90}that's 100 more than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.73,0:25:48.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且我还有个福克斯没有的功能\N{\fs90}But there's something else on here that's missing on his Focus,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.20,0:25:50.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,叫做 弹射预备\N{\fs90}and it's this - "line lock".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.57,0:25:53.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,启动 按住OK键开始初始化\N{\fs90}So, engage it.Press OK to initialise.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.97,0:25:56.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,正在初始化 初始化完成\N{\fs90}"Initialising.Initialising complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.21,0:25:58.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,确认后踩住刹车启动\N{\fs90}Firmly apply and hold brake to engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.31,0:26:01.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,已启动 按OK键开始\N{\fs90}Engaged. Press OK to begin."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.06,0:26:06.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,我现在锁住了前轮制动\N{\fs90}What that's doing is locking the front brakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.44,0:26:08.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,这样就可以暖胎了\N{\fs90}so I can warm up my tyres.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.02,0:26:12.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个功能对那种人来说非常理想 \N{\fs90}Hm. That is an ideal feature
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.71,0:26:14.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们每天睁开眼睛就会想\N{\fs90}for people who wake up in the morning and think
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.88,0:26:17.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得我的轮胎花纹太深了\N{\fs90}"Do you know, I've got too much tread on my tyres."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.03,0:26:27.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈哈 烧胎变得如此简单\N{\fs90}Yeah!I'm doing that automatically!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.61,0:26:35.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,太蠢了\N{\fs90}What a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.24,0:26:38.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,暖胎完毕之后\N{\fs90}With my tyres warmed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.15,0:26:40.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,我把车开到了起点线\N{\fs90}I took my place on the start line.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.84,0:26:47.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,好了 赛道模式 弹射起步\N{\fs90}Right, race mode, launch control,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.73,0:26:50.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,带超增压技术的涡轮\N{\fs90}over-boost facility on the turbocharger,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.90,0:26:52.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,四轮驱动 \N{\fs90}four-wheel-drive
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.11,0:26:55.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,以及一位拥有闪电反应的驾驶员\N{\fs90}and a man with lightning actions at the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.04,0:27:00.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,这辆车会像春天的羔羊一样蹿出去\N{\fs90}This car is going to boing off the line like a spring lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.68,0:27:04.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,开启弹射起步 挂入一档 \N{\fs90}Launch control, first gear
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.76,0:27:06.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,我准备好了\N{\fs90}and we're ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.74,0:27:26.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 他领先了\N{\fs90}Oh, he's away first.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.73,0:27:29.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,世界上最棒的弹射起步\N{\fs90}The most incredible launch control in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.84,0:27:33.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,加油啊\N{\fs90}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.68,0:27:36.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,加油 杰里米 你就要赢了\N{\fs90}Come on, Jeremy. Come on. You're winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.08,0:27:39.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,追上他了\N{\fs90}Oh, reeling him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.55,0:27:50.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 不 这不可能\N{\fs90}No, no, no! That's simply impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.96,0:27:53.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢他的参与\N{\fs90}Well, bless him for trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.18,0:28:00.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,我现在最不想看到的就是 他\N{\fs90}Things I don't want to see right now - number one, him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.75,0:28:02.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,那个啥 我赢了\N{\fs90}So er... I won, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.64,0:28:08.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我知道 但你的车没有漂移按钮 -什么按钮\N{\fs90}-Yes, but your car doesn't have a drift button.-A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.27,0:28:09.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,-漂移按钮 -干嘛用的\N{\fs90}-A drift button.-What does that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.96,0:28:11.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,你按下漂移按钮之后\N{\fs90}Well, you push it,and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.31,0:28:14.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,过弯的时候就可以漂移\N{\fs90}when you go round a corner,the car drifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.78,0:28:15.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,-真的吗 -真的\N{\fs90}-Does it?-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.04,0:28:17.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我很想见识一下\N{\fs90}You know, I'd love to see that in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.87,0:28:19.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我想看你漂移 -没问题\N{\fs90}-I'd love to see you doing that.-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.90,0:28:22.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,-给我演示一下 我想看 -你在这儿看好了\N{\fs90}-I'll watch. Yeah, show me.-You stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.36,0:28:25.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,有了它 就连詹姆斯 梅都能漂移\N{\fs90}You will not... Even James May could drift this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.29,0:28:27.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我来也 -我等不及了\N{\fs90}-Here we go!-I can't wait to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.34,0:28:38.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,看呐 女士们先生们\N{\fs90}Check it out,ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.57,0:28:40.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,好好看看\N{\fs90}Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.14,0:28:42.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,我在漂移\N{\fs90}I'm drifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.49,0:28:45.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样 哈蒙德 瞧\N{\fs90}What do you think of that, Hammond? Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.10,0:28:52.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德\N{\fs90}Hammond?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.05,0:28:56.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,人呢\N{\fs90}Hammond?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.01,0:28:59.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德\N{\fs90}Hammond!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.40,0:29:09.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么了 你不会怪我吧\N{\fs90}What?You're not gonna blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.50,0:29:10.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,你跑哪儿去了\N{\fs90}-Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.93,0:29:13.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,我走了 因为你太蠢\N{\fs90}Well, I left you because you were being moronic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.41,0:29:15.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我没有 -你就是\N{\fs90}-I wasn't!g-You were!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.07,0:29:16.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,说实话 如果你能买得起\N{\fs90}Seriously,who is going to buy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.41,0:29:18.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,V8引擎的野马 谁会去买\N{\fs90}a Ford Focus when,for the same money,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.07,0:29:19.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,价钱一样的福克斯啊\N{\fs90}you could havea V8-engine Mustang?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.84,0:29:21.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,-没人 -什么\N{\fs90}-No-one.-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.65,0:29:24.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,没人会买福克斯 野马太有个性了\N{\fs90}Nobody would. Mustang's got so much more character.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.05,0:29:26.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,等一下 你同意我说的吗\N{\fs90}Hang on.So, you agree with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.75,0:29:28.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,当然了 如果让我选\N{\fs90}Oh, God, yes! If I had the choice of those two cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.69,0:29:30.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,我每次都会选择野马\N{\fs90}I'd have the Mustang every day of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.43,0:29:35.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以你是毫无理由地毁了我的一天\N{\fs90}So you ruined my day out for no reason at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.57,0:29:39.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,可是给你的一天添堵 很有意思啊\N{\fs90}I ruined your day out because it was fun...to ruin your day out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.60,0:29:41.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,-干得漂亮 -没错 对不住了\N{\fs90}-Good work.-It was good work.Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.93,0:29:43.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在该来看看这两辆福特\N{\fs90}But anyway, we must now find out
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.99,0:29:46.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,在我们赛道上的表现了\N{\fs90}how fast those Fords go round our track,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.51,0:29:48.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,也就是说要把它们交给\N{\fs90}and that, of course, means handing them over
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.05,0:29:51.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的另一位美国同事\N{\fs90} to our other resident American -
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.21,0:29:55.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,他觉得沐浴露基本上就是共产党\N{\fs90}a man who thinks that shower gel is basically communist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.99,0:29:57.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,有请老美\N{\fs90}It's the American.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.72,0:30:00.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,他在那儿 看上去有点困惑\N{\fs90}There he is, looking bewildered.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.02,0:30:03.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,他出发了\N{\fs90}And he's away!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.52,0:30:07.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,听起来像是有一群老鼠堵在排气管里\N{\fs90}It sounds like a bunch of goddamn mice in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.73,0:30:13.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们为什么就不能用8个气缸呢\N{\fs90}Why the hell don't they just start with eight cylinders?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.67,0:30:18.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,我没见过这么奇怪的老鼠 他驶入了不直道\N{\fs90}Strangest mice I ever heard, as he powers down the Isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.87,0:30:20.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,声浪听着不错\N{\fs90}That is a good noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.77,0:30:23.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,握着方向盘的两只胳膊就像是和这辆车较劲\N{\fs90}Arms working the wheel like he's wrestling a drifter,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.98,0:30:25.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,不过也确实如此\N{\fs90}which, of course, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.48,0:30:27.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,这时他已经来到了留你名弯\N{\fs90}And already he's at Your Name Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.65,0:30:30.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,轮胎发出了尖叫 但依然牢牢抓着地面\N{\fs90}Tyres squealing, but it's clinging on well,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.45,0:30:32.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后上坡回到不直道\N{\fs90}and now the climb back onto the Isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.65,0:30:34.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车的空间太小了\N{\fs90}It ain't got no room in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.59,0:30:37.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有放啤酒的地方\N{\fs90}No place to put your beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.96,0:30:42.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得他和我放在车里的东西有点不一样\N{\fs90}I think he and I look for slightly different things in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.16,0:30:44.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 现在大力刹车\N{\fs90}Anyway, now hard on the brakes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.43,0:30:48.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,进入老奶房弯\N{\fs90}as he turns into Old Lady's House.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.07,0:30:50.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,在他的操控之下一切平稳\N{\fs90}Yeah, he is dispatching that with no dramas,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.90,0:30:52.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在他可以勇往直前\N{\fs90}and now he can get the hammer down
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.97,0:30:55.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,通过颠簸路段来到变电箱弯\N{\fs90}for the bumpy sprint to Substation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.31,0:30:56.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,看起来不错\N{\fs90}Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.84,0:30:58.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,四轮驱动的车会出现转向不足\N{\fs90}Four-wheel-drive cars can, of course, understeer,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.94,0:31:02.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,但在这里并没有出现\N{\fs90}but... nope, not a whiff of it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.28,0:31:06.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,干净利落地通过绵羊坡\N{\fs90}And Field Of Sheep, tidy through there as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.29,0:31:07.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后冲线了\N{\fs90}and across the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.02,0:31:12.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得他应该会喜欢这辆车\N{\fs90}Now, I think he might enjoy this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.46,0:31:14.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,的确如此 响胎起步\N{\fs90}And he is wheel-spinning away!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.30,0:31:18.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就对了 我爱美国肌肉车\N{\fs90}All right! American muscle, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.77,0:31:22.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,5.0升的野马 这家伙可不好惹\N{\fs90}5.0 Mustang - this thing is badass.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.01,0:31:28.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有个大后备箱 可以装我的高尔夫球杆\N{\fs90}It's got a trunk, place for my golf clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.81,0:31:30.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,带上我家娘们 \N{\fs90}Pack up the old lady
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.15,0:31:32.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,周末开车出去玩\N{\fs90} go for the weekend somewhere in this thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.45,0:31:34.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,想甩尾巴就能甩\N{\fs90}and you can haul ass while you're goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.85,0:31:38.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,他说了些关于老女人和甩屁股的事\N{\fs90}Something there about an old lady and hauling a bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.58,0:31:39.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,驶入不直道\N{\fs90}Anyway, he's on the Isn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.85,0:31:42.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,飞一般地冲进留你名弯\N{\fs90}and he's flying into Your Name Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.46,0:31:45.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,强大的野马让老美充满了活力\N{\fs90}The mighty Mustang has filled the American with vigour,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.79,0:31:47.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个弯他处理得异常简练\N{\fs90}and he's being surprisingly tidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.33,0:31:54.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,这才是美国人要的 我们就想烧胎\N{\fs90}That's what us Americans want, we want to smoke the tyres.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.87,0:31:58.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,甭废话 就该这么来\N{\fs90}We want this thing to just get shit and get.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.50,0:32:02.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,我实在不知道他在说什么 只听到了噪音\N{\fs90}Literally no idea what he's on about. It's just a noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.17,0:32:05.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车刹车贼强 说停就停\N{\fs90}When this thing stops, man, it stops on a dime.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.35,0:32:09.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,刹车特牛 一秒就停\N{\fs90}"It'll stop on a dime and give you nine cents change" is what we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.18,0:32:11.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,你根本没办法让他闭嘴\N{\fs90}You really can't shut him up about this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.35,0:32:15.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,好了 干净得通过了老奶房弯\N{\fs90}Anyway, he is keeping it neat round Old Lady's House,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.09,0:32:18.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后释放出V8的狂怒\N{\fs90}and then unleashing that V8 fury
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.56,0:32:21.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,一路杀到了变电箱弯\N{\fs90}over the rough stuff to Substation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.09,0:32:24.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,大力踩下刹车 准备90度左弯\N{\fs90}Hard on the brakes, ready for the 90 left.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.70,0:32:26.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,驶过绵羊坡\N{\fs90}Blip it up to Field Of Sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.87,0:32:28.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,他来了\N{\fs90}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.27,0:32:32.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,霸气地甩了车尾 冲线\N{\fs90}Flurry of exuberance, and across the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.37,0:32:34.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\fs90}There we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.85,0:32:38.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,好了 这是圈速榜\N{\fs90}OK, here's the Lap Board.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.94,0:32:43.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们先来看看福克斯的成绩\N{\fs90}Let's have a look, first of all, where the Focus went.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.25,0:32:44.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,在哪\N{\fs90}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.02,0:32:46.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 在这儿\N{\fs90}Oh, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.49,0:32:48.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,比ST200快 并不意外\N{\fs90}Faster than an ST200 - perhaps not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.95,0:32:49.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,本该如此\N{\fs90}Just as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.92,0:32:53.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在看看野马的表现\N{\fs90}Now let's bring up the Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.29,0:32:54.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs90}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.93,0:32:59.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,这一点也不尴尬对吧\N{\fs90}- That's not embarrassing, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.87,0:33:03.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,你 我还有老美都喜欢的车\N{\fs90}The car that you, me, and the American all prefer
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.94,0:33:07.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,比欧洲血统的福克斯慢了很多\N{\fs90}is quite a lot slower than the European Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.24,0:33:08.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs90}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.54,0:33:10.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,好了 听我说 我们继续节目吧\N{\fs90}Anyway, listen,let's move on, shall we,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.76,0:33:13.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,下面是 明星脑碰脑\N{\fs90}to Celebrity Brain Crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.20,0:33:21.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\fs90}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.29,0:33:26.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,本周的嘉宾 不仅是我最喜欢的F1车手\N{\fs90}our guest this week isn't just my favourite Formula One driver,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.59,0:33:28.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,还是个芬兰本地小伙\N{\fs90}he's also a local boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.86,0:33:32.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 他就是赛车界的话唠\N{\fs90}Oh, yeah, this is the chatty man of motorsport,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.67,0:33:34.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,根本停不下来先生\N{\fs90}Mr Effervescent,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.29,0:33:36.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 有请基米 莱科宁\N{\fs90}ladies and gentlemen, Kimi Räikkönen!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.44,0:33:39.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,他来了\N{\fs90}Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.37,0:33:44.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们一会儿要问他什么\N{\fs90}What are we gonna ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.44,0:33:46.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,你问他什么都不重要\N{\fs90}It doesn't matter what you ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.11,0:33:49.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你根本得不到一个连贯的答案\N{\fs90}It doesn't, because you won't get a coherent answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.78,0:33:51.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,他没事吧\N{\fs90}Is he all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.29,0:33:55.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,等一下 噢不\N{\fs90}No, hang on. Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.74,0:33:57.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,-噢不 -又是这样\N{\fs90}- Oh, no. - Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.28,0:34:01.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 女士们先生们\N{\fs90}No, he has, I'm afraid, ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.93,0:34:04.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,莱科宁因饮酒过量而死\N{\fs90}literally drunk himself to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.08,0:34:06.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,见鬼\N{\fs90}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.83,0:34:09.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是说 他来不成了?\N{\fs90}- Does that mean he's not coming on, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.31,0:34:11.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,当然 他肝中毒了\N{\fs90}Well, his liver has failed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.09,0:34:12.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且他正在北极圈冰冷的黄昏中\N{\fs90}and he's now slowly solidifying
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.82,0:34:16.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,逐渐僵硬 所以没错 他来不了\N{\fs90}in the freezing dusk of an Arctic night, so that's a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.34,0:34:18.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,没事 无所谓\N{\fs90}Yeah, but it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.16,0:34:20.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,其实有所谓 我还是挺喜欢他的\N{\fs90}Well, it does, cos I actually rather liked Kimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.68,0:34:24.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,不过我可以想出点其他事情\N{\fs90}But I can think of something else we can do to fill the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.13,0:34:26.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,是这样的 如果你现在\N{\fs90}Here's the thing.Er... If you're watching this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.55,0:34:29.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,正在收看这个节目 时间应该\N{\fs90}on the day the programme is actually released,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.19,0:34:31.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,已经是12月23日了\N{\fs90}it is December 23rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.82,0:34:34.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,距离圣诞节只剩两天\N{\fs90}There are two days to go until Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.09,0:34:35.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你是个男人 \N{\fs90}and if you're a man
