Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.54,0:43:09.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,这真是个好东西 不过没关系\N{\fs90}That was... That was a brilliant idea, but never mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.51,0:43:12.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,我这里有一份最棒的圣诞礼物\N{\fs90}because erm... I have a perfect Christmas present here.
