Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.78,0:43:50.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,鲍勃 我们在这边\N{\fs90}Bob! We're over here, Bob!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.45,0:43:52.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,-鲍勃 -转过来\N{\fs90}-Bob! -Bob, we're over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.18,0:43:53.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你们在哪儿 -他在那儿\N{\fs90}-Where are you? -He's there!
